<li>W. A. E Skurnik, <i>African Political Thought: Lumumba, Nkrumah, Touré</i> (Social Science Foundation and <a href="/wiki/Graduate_School_of_International_Studies" title="Graduate School of International Studies">Graduate School of International Studies</a>, <a href="/wiki/University_of_Denver" title="University of Denver">University of Denver</a>. Monograph series in world affairs, v. 5, no. 3-4), 1968, Denver: University of Denver, ASIN B0006CNYSW</li>
