<li>Thomas R. Kanza, <i>Conflict in the Congo: The Rise and Fall of Lumumba</i> (Penguin African library), 1972, New York: Penguin, <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0140410309" class="internal">ISBN 0-14-041030-9</a></li>
